  "author_association": "NONE",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "For blocks where `block.number >= DAO_TOKEN_REFUND`, make the following changes:\n\nNo transaction may increase the eth balance of a contract deployed after `DAO_TOKEN_REFUND` above 100,000. Any such transaction should fail and send all gas to the miner.\n",
